From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Nickel Browser: Fingerprint Protection

This patch implements comprehensive fingerprint protection:
- Canvas noise injection
- WebGL vendor/renderer spoofing
- AudioContext noise
- Client rects randomization
- Font enumeration blocking
- Hardware API spoofing
- Screen resolution spoofing
- Battery API blocking
- Sensor API blocking

